42:35.011 --> 42:37.723
O'Connor gave that to you.

42:37.723 --> 42:39.224
He gave me one, too.

42:39.224 --> 42:40.934
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

42:40.934 --> 42:45.188
It belongs at the bottom
of the Charles, where mine is.

42:45.188 --> 42:49.192
Don't you get that thing
fucking anywhere near her.

42:49.192 --> 42:53.613
What's the matter with you?

42:53.613 --> 42:56.659
You fucking drunk?

42:56.659 --> 42:59.452
You're not taking this shit
seriously.

43:12.132 --> 43:15.343
[Daryll]
What's wrong with him?

43:15.343 --> 43:17.178
You guys want
to hear Bridget sing?

43:17.178 --> 43:21.016
- [Bridget] Mom, stop it.
- [Abby] Come on, Bridge.

43:21.016 --> 43:23.685
[Darryl] It'd be kind of
great right now, Bridge.

43:23.685 --> 43:24.978
[Bridget] Okay, okay.
Yeah.

43:24.978 --> 43:26.354
[Abby]
Yeah.

43:29.399 --> 43:32.778
[Bridget playing guitar]
♪ They poured a round ♪

43:32.778 --> 43:35.238
♪ For the sailor ♪

43:35.238 --> 43:38.450
♪ And they heard his tale ♪

43:38.450 --> 43:39.617
♪ Of a world ♪

43:39.617 --> 43:43.747
♪ That was so far away ♪

43:43.747 --> 43:45.040
♪ And a song ♪

43:45.040 --> 43:49.586
♪ That we'd never heard ♪

43:49.586 --> 43:52.255
♪ A song of a little bird ♪

43:52.255 --> 43:54.841
[phone vibrates]

43:54.841 --> 43:57.761
♪ That fell in love ♪

43:57.761 --> 44:00.513
♪ With a whale ♪

44:00.513 --> 44:02.891
♪ He says you cannot live
in the ocean... ♪

44:02.891 --> 44:04.809
Yeah.

44:04.809 --> 44:06.561
[electronic voice] Men's Central
Jail collect call from...

44:06.561 --> 44:07.353
[Mickey]
Mickey Donovan.

44:07.353 --> 44:08.480
Yeah.

44:08.480 --> 44:09.939
[phone beeps]

44:09.939 --> 44:12.734
[Mickey]
Ray, you there?

44:12.734 --> 44:14.778
Hey, Mick.

44:14.778 --> 44:17.989
How was the baptism?

44:17.989 --> 44:21.869
[Ray]
Fine.

44:21.869 --> 44:25.080
Bridget and Connor
doing all right?

44:25.080 --> 44:28.416
[Ray]
Good.

44:28.416 --> 44:31.377
Abby's health?

44:31.377 --> 44:33.756
She's good.

44:33.756 --> 44:35.131
[Mickey]
Good.

44:35.131 --> 44:37.718
I talked to your lawyer friend,
the Jew.

44:37.718 --> 44:40.512
He said, uh,

44:40.512 --> 44:42.889
he could get
my charges reduced

44:42.889 --> 44:45.141
from eight counts
down to three,

44:45.141 --> 44:48.728
get the death sentence
thrown out.

44:48.728 --> 44:50.480
Fuck, Mick.

44:50.480 --> 44:53.441
Bright side, I'll be out of here
when I'm 310.

44:53.441 --> 44:55.443
[laughs]

44:58.154 --> 45:00.365
[sighs]

45:00.365 --> 45:03.034
I'll tell you, in here,

45:03.034 --> 45:07.997
I've been thinking about life,
about what matters.

45:07.997 --> 45:11.042
The only fucking permanent thing
is love.

45:11.042 --> 45:13.253
Why men build skyscrapers,

45:13.253 --> 45:16.422
make art, go to war.

45:16.422 --> 45:19.467
Love.

45:19.467 --> 45:21.719
Mick?

45:21.719 --> 45:24.347
[Mickey]
Yeah?

45:32.230 --> 45:36.151
Thanks.

45:36.151 --> 45:38.904
Kiss that baby for me.

45:38.904 --> 45:41.322
Eh?

45:43.908 --> 45:47.745
[exhales sharply]

45:47.745 --> 45:50.290
[Bridget] ♪ And a bird ♪

45:50.290 --> 45:53.543
♪ On the tide ♪

45:53.543 --> 45:58.006
♪ Oh, please don't cry ♪

45:58.006 --> 46:00.801
♪ Let me dry ♪

46:00.801 --> 46:03.636
♪ Your eyes ♪

46:03.636 --> 46:08.099
♪ So tell me
that you'll wait for me ♪

46:08.099 --> 46:11.644
♪ Hold me in your arms ♪

46:11.644 --> 46:13.688
♪ I promise we never
will part ♪

46:13.688 --> 46:17.066
[phone chimes]

46:17.066 --> 46:21.863
♪ I'll never sail
back to the time ♪

46:21.863 --> 46:24.908
♪ But I'll always pretend ♪

46:24.908 --> 46:27.535
♪ You're mine... ♪

46:27.535 --> 46:30.538
[Russian hip-hop music
from house speakers]

46:30.538 --> 46:35.543
♪♪♪

46:50.600 --> 46:55.605
♪♪♪

47:11.829 --> 47:16.793
♪♪♪

47:16.793 --> 47:19.796
[lemur chirps]

47:32.225 --> 47:37.230
♪♪♪

47:44.946 --> 47:46.864
Ray Donovan.

47:46.864 --> 47:49.158
You have come back.

47:54.247 --> 47:57.458
Sonia wanted me
to give you this.

47:57.458 --> 47:59.877
She told me to apologize.

47:59.877 --> 48:04.632
Told me to tell you there's
an extra hundred grand there.

48:04.632 --> 48:08.136
For any problems
I might have caused.

48:08.136 --> 48:11.222
You are a what?

48:11.222 --> 48:13.016
Excuse me?

48:13.016 --> 48:17.937
For a living,
you are a useful man.

48:17.937 --> 48:20.606
I don't know what the fuck
you're talking about.

48:20.606 --> 48:22.984
You've been useful
for Sonia.

48:22.984 --> 48:26.738
Now be useful to me.

48:26.738 --> 48:29.074
Take the money.

48:29.074 --> 48:33.078
You be useful to me.

48:36.831 --> 48:40.251
The girl with the string.

48:42.295 --> 48:44.672
We had a party.

48:44.672 --> 48:46.091
Party got bad.

48:46.091 --> 48:48.634
She got excited
and she break her neck.

48:48.634 --> 48:51.637
♪ ominous music ♪

48:51.637 --> 48:54.515
♪♪♪

48:54.515 --> 48:57.310
You take the painting
to the port, yes?

48:57.310 --> 48:59.854
We take the girl, too.

48:59.854 --> 49:01.689
Ship her back to my people
in Moscow.

49:01.689 --> 49:04.151
They will dispose.

49:04.151 --> 49:06.402
I take you.

49:06.402 --> 49:08.237
You help me
ship the girl.

49:08.237 --> 49:10.031
[sniffs]

49:10.031 --> 49:15.036
♪♪♪

49:21.126 --> 49:22.085
[gunshots]

49:22.085 --> 49:23.461
- Whoa!
- Oh!

49:23.461 --> 49:25.505
Oh, fuck.
Oh.

49:25.505 --> 49:27.132
[dog barks]

49:27.132 --> 49:29.675
[Larry]
What the fuck?

49:29.675 --> 49:31.178
Oh, yeah?

49:31.178 --> 49:33.137
You better run,
you fucking assholes.

49:33.137 --> 49:34.680
I see you, Donovan.

49:34.680 --> 49:38.185
[rifle barrel clicking]
I see you.

49:38.185 --> 49:41.062
[huffs]

49:41.062 --> 49:45.316
Your father is a funny man.

49:45.316 --> 49:48.736
I guess.

49:48.736 --> 49:51.114
I will take care of his safety
in prison.

49:54.617 --> 49:57.829
You should be glad he took care
of this problem for you.

49:59.330 --> 50:03.000
You should be thankful.

50:05.545 --> 50:07.463
Thankful.

50:13.344 --> 50:17.557
[baby whines]

50:17.557 --> 50:18.349
Okay.

50:18.349 --> 50:23.146
You okay?

50:23.146 --> 50:25.232
Fucking drunk.

50:25.232 --> 50:28.192
Give her to me
before you drop her.

50:28.192 --> 50:31.113
Come on.

50:31.113 --> 50:32.197
Bunchy.

50:32.197 --> 50:35.075
[baby groans]

50:35.075 --> 50:37.244
Hey.

50:37.244 --> 50:40.079
There.
There she is.

50:40.079 --> 50:42.748
Hey.

50:42.748 --> 50:44.917
Oh.

50:50.882 --> 50:52.925
What?

50:52.925 --> 50:54.635
You got cancer,
don't you?

50:54.635 --> 50:56.512
What?

50:56.512 --> 50:58.265
Don't you lie to me.

50:58.265 --> 51:01.268
[baby fusses]

51:01.268 --> 51:05.771
Shh.

51:05.771 --> 51:08.191
Bunch, it's not that bad.

51:10.985 --> 51:13.279
You can't get sick!

51:13.279 --> 51:14.655
Bunchy.

51:14.655 --> 51:16.241
I love you, Abby.

51:16.241 --> 51:18.826
You're my best friend.
You can't get sick.

51:18.826 --> 51:19.827
Come on, Bunch--

51:19.827 --> 51:21.163
You can't die, you hear me?

51:21.163 --> 51:24.124
You can't die!

51:24.124 --> 51:26.959
Are you fucking kidding me?

51:26.959 --> 51:30.046
I am gonna
live forever.

51:30.046 --> 51:32.089
Don't you worry
about it.

51:35.177 --> 51:39.264
Come here.

51:39.264 --> 51:42.767
You're just drunk, is all.

51:42.767 --> 51:44.977
And you're tired.

51:44.977 --> 51:47.104
Just go to bed.

51:47.104 --> 51:48.689
Come here.

51:48.689 --> 51:51.025
- I know.
- [Bunchy crying]

51:51.025 --> 51:52.152
Honey.

51:52.152 --> 51:53.319
Bunchy.

51:53.319 --> 51:54.320
I'll take care
of Maria.

51:54.320 --> 51:56.155
Come on.

51:56.155 --> 51:58.115
Oh, Bunchy.
Go to bed.

51:58.115 --> 52:00.243
Come on.

52:00.243 --> 52:02.787
Come on, honey.

52:02.787 --> 52:04.872
I got her.

52:10.878 --> 52:12.964
Yeah.

52:12.964 --> 52:14.507
That's right.

52:14.507 --> 52:16.509
I know.
I know.

52:16.509 --> 52:19.637
Everyone in life
has a story.

52:19.637 --> 52:22.307
Hers...

52:22.307 --> 52:25.310
...is very short story.

52:29.356 --> 52:33.818
Put the girl
in that crate.

52:33.818 --> 52:36.112
Seal it up
and see the custom man.

52:36.112 --> 52:39.031
He'll do the rest.

52:39.031 --> 52:40.825
In there.

52:40.825 --> 52:42.743
You understand?

52:46.163 --> 52:49.376
Be useful.
We can be friends.

52:49.376 --> 52:51.627
Sure.

52:51.627 --> 52:54.463
We can be friends.

52:54.463 --> 52:56.757
[grunting]

52:56.757 --> 52:59.760
[screaming]

53:13.024 --> 53:15.484
Look at me.

53:15.484 --> 53:19.697
Look at me!

53:19.697 --> 53:22.700
[gunshot]

53:22.700 --> 53:27.747
♪♪♪

53:39.384 --> 53:43.179
[baby fusses]

53:43.179 --> 53:44.847
No?

53:44.847 --> 53:45.973
No?

53:45.973 --> 53:47.808
You don't want it?

53:51.396 --> 53:52.855
[sighs]

53:52.855 --> 53:56.692
It's not gonna do you
much good, sweetheart.

53:56.692 --> 53:58.986
Knock yourself out.

53:58.986 --> 54:01.323
[baby suckling]

54:03.324 --> 54:06.243
[phone rings]

54:12.292 --> 54:13.250
[Ray]
Yeah?

54:13.250 --> 54:17.755
How was your talk with Ivan?

54:17.755 --> 54:21.676
Was he pleased that you came?

54:21.676 --> 54:25.429
Sure.

54:25.429 --> 54:29.476
Then everything's
back to the way that it was.

54:29.476 --> 54:32.269
Sure.

54:32.269 --> 54:35.648
[Sonia] I'll see to it that he
looks after your father, Ray.

54:35.648 --> 54:37.650
After everything
that you've done for me,

54:37.650 --> 54:42.655
I'll see to it Ivan makes sure
your father is safe.

54:42.655 --> 54:44.865
♪ solemn music ♪

54:44.865 --> 54:45.658
[phone beeps]

54:45.658 --> 54:47.410
♪♪♪

54:47.410 --> 54:51.373
Ray?

55:03.759 --> 55:08.723
♪♪♪

55:22.445 --> 55:27.450
♪♪♪

55:42.506 --> 55:45.134
♪♪♪

55:45.134 --> 55:48.137
[engine turns over]

55:48.137 --> 55:53.142
♪♪♪

56:05.446 --> 56:10.451
♪♪♪
